Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 在場的10位同學無法出席今年的競演會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 請將此視作令各位更上一層樓的良機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻各位心中的那份不甘和悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是競演會成員所沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這同時也說明各位已經變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將這種心情謹記於心 勤於練習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定能變得比現在更加優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位將這次的經歷 化作各自的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後完成各自的飛躍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 長笛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上低音號的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}圓號的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 圓號的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就是這首曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 讓我們眼下這些人通過練習 最終能夠演奏該曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是單簧管和…大號的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼 單簧管的應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單簧管的給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過老師也真是會說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他那麼一講 自然會湧出幹勁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個帥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎？我倒不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}咦？圓號？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓號是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事 是帥哥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來所有人就都拿到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼趕緊搬樂器過來 開始練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我記得部長說 要在開始之前先決定好名字來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
