Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還全給寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊名要能體現出我們這十人才有的個性呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}大五郎的話個性滿滿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}十個人跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的頭文字組合起來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}循序漸進一點點來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yo ka hi hu mo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,na ta ka na ka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒個完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只把學姐們的姓名首字母組合起來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高2的有中川夏紀 森田忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是我 加部友惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,na mo ka…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ka mo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mo na ka！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最中！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺不錯的嘛！最中小隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 難道不覺得像諧星組合嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是摩納哥公國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：摩納哥日語發音monako
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 也不是王國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為可愛很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只到競演會結束為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們小隊的隊名就決定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“最中小隊”了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？最中？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是最中？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於青春的當下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:55.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：當下的日文漢字也是最中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似這樣的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是把高2學生的姓名首字母拼了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的 又好記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請鄭重地說上一句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜上 我們最中小隊接下來也將著眼競演會與各位共同努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼能幫上忙的 請儘管說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…緊張死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 像這樣不能參加合奏練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人重新認識到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己落選了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滝老師不也說過了嗎 讓我們把這份不甘使到練習中去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們也還有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:56.36,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fr-15\fry30\move(172,455,268,455)}最中\N決定!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起好好練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧 加油 最中！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隊名很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卓帕…卡布拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 葉月醬 說是在2樓練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩誰沒通知來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠氣勢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練…練習怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…現在是休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 我來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不用啦 而且也有小輪子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要下了樓就輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫你搬下樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能幫我拖住下面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人搬這個果然還是很辛苦的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤你是從高中開始參加吹奏樂部的來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前告訴過你哦 就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼…我有問過你為什麼選大號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還沒問過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 最開始我是想選小號的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被明日香學姐騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？被騙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說什麼“是你命運的搭檔”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冢本一直選的長號？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 初中的時候是圓號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 但你長號吹得挺好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:06.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那邊的你 青春就是吹奏樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從以前就一直想吹長號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡爵士長號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冢本！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你練習加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來久美子她感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子醬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你看 因為練習不同所以不能經常在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是普普通通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在自由選曲上有地方吹不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我問的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 合奏的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冢本不是就在她旁邊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怎麼說呢 各種意義上有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 葉月醬你是要…搶婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 請說實話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 喜歡上一個人是不需要規則的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠輝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想那兩個人因為我而彆彆扭扭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得如果我插嘴 反而會搞得更僵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事啊 我最不擅長了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直覺得戀愛什麼的很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒告白就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比什麼都不做要好太多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月醬可厲害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超帥氣 超可愛的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們去便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 又要去扭樂器扭蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我請你吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要不要選個貴的冰淇淋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心意寄託在上面 送給參加競演會的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有在電視上看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手製作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我在考慮弄點吉祥物上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要想50多種不會很辛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分工一下應該沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我覺得可愛的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這裡果然還是呼應隊名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這樣如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也請教教羅羅訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能發覺得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要這樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這邊稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競演會落選的時候還以為稍微變清閒點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙一點比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒著的話相對地也會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 剛才拿走的是誰的簽？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的 誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是我的錯覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏紀學姐有和男人交往過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有上低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是久美子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎麼了 這麼突然？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼地 覺得你很惹人憐愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能對你說的也只有“不要留下遺憾”這麼一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能加入低音部真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼細心打包 然後和昨天的一起搬到走廊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！x2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 葉月醬 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 久美子 高坂同學 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 兩位的制服都好乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 送去店裡洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好x2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢高昂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超高昂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸巾也換了根新的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我就料到可能會出這種狀況 就帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不妙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是超賣力地練習了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至都流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連在河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久我也聽到了練習聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 會全力支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 繫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊吧 不是還要試音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我可以幫忙搬的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把打擊樂器搬進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧 該搬大號了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 初學者也該畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冢本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是大號嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士也開走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最中小隊稍微收拾下音樂教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後坐電車前往會場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達會場之後按剛才討論好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意器材搬運的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方搞砸了的話也會影響到演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們好好幹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最中 最中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要喊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最中…加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為愛的捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有塞東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是大吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是驚喜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 裡面真的有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是冢本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哦 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個 可是特別款式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊 冢本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名來真煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？這是鬧得哪一出啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會想辦法的 待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是把最大隻的木槌 忘在教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 好像誰都不在學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是時間已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會坐後面的電車追上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等你來哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 畢竟是加藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏紀學姐為什麼加入了吹奏樂部？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢 加藤你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:19:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為給人感覺…又高貴又帥氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不高貴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但練習很辛苦 也遠說不上高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感到很慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓我再選一次 我想我還是會選吹奏樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大吉 我會全力支持你的 儘管上吧！！ 祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧了…大號手的肺活量啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按平時那樣上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}怎麼樣？沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趕快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是過意不去 加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不 沒事 總之請加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}謝謝 真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用跑的去取來了木槌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小綠 請你展現出最棒的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北宇治的各位 有請
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了
